result.name: Jade Garden

reviews.text:
Jade garden is one of my favourite restaurants. Roasted goose and roasted pork are their signature dishes. Booking is not required for normal weekdays. If you are lucky to be seated next to the window, you may see the light show at 8 pm across the Victoria harbour.

The price is fair enough consider the location. The food quality is good compared with other Chinese restaurant in tst. 

No tip is required as it is included in the bill.

Except from a bad service food was good.
They are not welcoming to foreigner s like me..
Everyone was seated and was welcomed with a jar of water and tea.
But our table was told we have to pay for water.
We keep on calling waiter or the supervisor for our food was almost consumed and last order hasn't arrived but they ignore us..

I end up approching the Manager and cancel the fried rice.

They are not friendly to foreigners
Very bad service
Amazing view of the HK skyline. Food was good and the service is decent.
One of my favourite Cantonese restaurants. They have decorated and lovely ambience. The menu prices went up to. Good for dim sum or evening meal.
Still offer great dimsum

result.name: 星光行

reviews.text:
老牌商廈，含商場及寫字樓。
亦有幾間美心集團食館及誠品店。地下有麥當奴漢堡飽店。
鄰近天星碼頭，腳程五分鐘可達香港文化中心及香港太空館，廿分鐘可步行至科學舘。
星光行 位於尖沙咀碼頭傍邊 商場面積吾算中型 但冇咩野行 樓上主要是寫字樓 有學聯 有出名的北京樓 但不是人人食得起 場內大部份店舖壽命不長 浪費了－個非常方便之商業地段 ！
觀光旅遊區，頗受遊客歡迎。
